doing, man?

00:20.354 --> 00:22.021
What are you--
whoa, whoa, whoa, whoa.

00:22.023 --> 00:24.256
What are you doing?
Are you okay?

00:24.258 --> 00:25.491
Let's go.

00:25.493 --> 00:27.659
Hey, stop, please. Jeez.
(tires screech)

00:27.661 --> 00:29.294
(horn blares)

00:29.296 --> 00:31.263
All right, you okay?

00:31.265 --> 00:34.099
What are you thinking?

00:34.101 --> 00:37.302
All right, let's, um...
(exhales)

00:37.304 --> 00:39.471
Let's get you off
your feet.

00:39.473 --> 00:41.340
Don't want anymore damage
to that ankle, right?

00:41.342 --> 00:43.609
Got that, buddy?
Got that?

00:43.611 --> 00:45.044
(groans)

00:45.046 --> 00:55.120
