of morphine, jackson.

01:04.565 --> 01:07.599
Thank you. Thank you.

01:07.601 --> 01:09.068
So you have no memory
whatsoever

01:09.070 --> 01:10.736
Wandering
into traffic like that?

01:10.738 --> 01:14.706
Mnh-mnh. I must've been groggy
from the surgery.

01:14.708 --> 01:17.209
