hit by a car out there.

01:17.211 --> 01:20.679
0.3 percent of patients
are injured while in hospital.

01:20.681 --> 01:22.548
Yeah. Ian's an actuary,
by the way.

01:22.550 --> 01:23.782
Uh, you work in insurance?

01:23.784 --> 01:26.652
