companies.

01:28.355 --> 01:29.755
Oh, you mean like how long
people live if they smoke?

01:29.757 --> 01:31.090
Stuff like that?

01:31.092 --> 01:34.860
Being an actuary's kind of like
being a cross between

01:34.862 --> 01:37.229
An undertaker and a booker.
(inhales sharply)

01:37.231 --> 01:39.765
Ooh!
Okay, you have really
cracked this plate

01:39.767 --> 01:41.633
That I put
in your ankle here.

01:41.635 --> 01:43.235
