01:43.237 --> 01:44.770
Thank you, jackson.
Uh, go ahead.

01:44.772 --> 01:46.205
Ask me anything.
I'll tell you how likely

01:46.207 --> 01:47.739
It is it'll happen to you.

01:47.741 --> 01:48.874
Getting bit by a snake.

01:48.876 --> 01:50.442
