by lightning.

01:50.444 --> 01:51.510
I wouldn't worry about it.

01:51.512 --> 01:52.744
I like this guy.
He's good.

01:52.746 --> 01:57.483
Odds of getting back together
with your ex-girlfriend.

01:57.485 --> 01:58.884
Why would you even ask...

01:58.886 --> 02:01.653
How would you describe
your sexual chemistry?

02:01.655 --> 02:03.755
