02:05.226 --> 02:07.493
How would you describe
their sexual chemistry?

02:07.495 --> 02:08.494
Eh, it's hot.

02:08.496 --> 02:10.562
Jackson!

02:10.564 --> 02:15.501
(alex breathes heavily)

02:15.503 --> 02:17.703
Hey...

02:17.705 --> 02:19.771
